BUGS
====

- sometimes there are unclosable empty windows
- the smartplacement is not perfect
- task menu width is sometimes too big
- application menus are sometimes not correctly placed
- when you use CycleWorkspace, and you switch to a window (Alt+Tab or with the task menu) you can not arrive to the correct workspace
- core dumps with bad config files.
- and more...

If you have any comments or if you see a bug, please report it (how you do it, what is your system's configuration  ...) to mulot_j@epita.fr

